{"tid":2488333,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[今次認真] 世衛將 \"強迫性手淫障礙\" 列為精神病","createTime":"2021-04-14T07:17:37.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-14T15:13:03.000Z","uid":353278,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e315c1c178897351845c6465be8ded0266afb422","tid":2488333,"uid":353278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T07:17:37.000Z","msg":"世界衛生組織對《國際疾病分類》進行了另一次修訂。在他們的修訂分類中，他們將強迫性手淫障礙 (COMPULSIVE MASTURBATION DISORDER) 識別為精神健康狀況。<br />\n<br />\n什麼是強迫性手淫？<br />\n表現所有強迫行為的一件事是缺乏衝動控制。另外，有反复的想法驅使該人進行手淫。它與強迫症類似，它始於強迫念頭，並導致強迫他們對這些念頭採取行動。但是，在強迫性手淫或任何其他強迫性行為中，這些想法涉及性幻想和性衝動。<br />\n<br />\n強迫性的跡象<br />\n強迫性手淫症會干擾一個人的社交生活，甚至會影響他們的身體健康。當一個人進行強迫性手淫時，他們所做的事情是有害的。由於該行為是強迫性的，因此該人會經常這樣做，以至於乾擾親密關係以及與所愛者的正常關係。或者可以突然衝刺，但以至於人身傷害自己。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins><em>一個人可能會繼續自慰，即使身體上有跡象表明有必要停下來，也可能不會停下來。</em></ins></strong>其他人只是將其作為日常工作的一部分，無法想像沒有它。每種行為背後的驅動力是圍繞動作的強迫。<br />\n<br />\n強迫症治療<br />\n強迫性手淫的根源是與性行為本身無關的精神疾病。從事這項活動的人沒有某些人認為的極端性慾。該行為滿足了另一種心理需求，因此需要心理和成癮治療。<br />\n<br />\n與這種行為有關的心理問題需要專業治療和康復環境。這種疾病需要與其他任何成癮所需的治療類型相同的治療。<strong><em><ins>有助於治愈和幫助治療強迫性手淫症的成癮療法包括：</ins></em></strong><br />\n整體療法<br />\n家庭療法<br />\n認知行為療法<br />\n辯證行為療法<br />\nEMDR<br />\n體驗療法<br />\n音樂療法<br />\n瑜伽療法<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.santecenter.com/addiction-treatment-programs/sex-addiction-treatment/compulsive-masturbation-disorder/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.santecenter.com%2Faddiction-treatment-programs%2Fsex-addiction-treatment%2Fcompulsive-masturbation-disorder%2F&d=t2%2FAN0mLur8%2Bj%2B1Tvbkzvh%2FwB%2Fd2Hr%2Bf%2F5fgrRWXORU%3D&h=ab61b823\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.santecenter.com/addiction-treatment-programs/sex-addiction-treatment/compulsive-masturbation-disorder/</a>"},{"pid":"939a1999088befc011e54642230e27adf7ca2bc5","tid":2488333,"uid":388418,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T07:18:33.000Z","msg":"吉蛇揸住千五個都要自己黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5fcca83dabad7e503ac1ad30d561ee32ab9f33e","tid":2488333,"uid":210333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T07:29:46.000Z","msg":"體驗療法係乜？"},{"pid":"d00ea7f837fdbb86c933a1a5fc53df503370c8f3","tid":2488333,"uid":353278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b5fcca83dabad7e503ac1ad30d561ee32ab9f33e","tid":2488333,"uid":210333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T07:29:46.000Z","msg":"體驗療法係乜？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T07:33:40.000Z","msg":"做下其他嘢分散自己注意力 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e64cab19e66a8023b704cfe6ffdf20554119ea3d","tid":2488333,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T07:34:42.000Z","msg":"又要打個飛機先"},{"pid":"14b862ed2b06dae19a2c52f30d69b3b7540508ec","tid":2488333,"uid":27077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T07:34:55.000Z","msg":"如果有 喺香港出唔出到白卡"},{"pid":"89a869e85f510bf9cb6b64c57f78652b5e8a9a26","tid":2488333,"uid":60535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T15:00:02.000Z","msg":"雖然我覺得蕭別離條撚樣係戇𨳊，但係我贊成男人係有時要節制下自己打飛機"},{"pid":"951f87d731e7ab93a8da3835da69f01630192bd3","tid":2488333,"uid":138138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"89a869e85f510bf9cb6b64c57f78652b5e8a9a26","tid":2488333,"uid":60535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T15:00:02.000Z","msg":"雖然我覺得蕭別離條撚樣係戇𨳊，但係我贊成男人係有時要節制下自己打飛機"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T15:13:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmYPpdAmtqk5Gwg1rPNbzJGY7Hix6p6JHtvjK4zdFhe8Tn?filename=KppYGyY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKppYGyY.png&h=d1e0efb1&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}